<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>發生錯誤</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="height: 100vh;">

    <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="display-1 fw-bold text-danger">Oops!</h1>
        <h2 class="h4 mb-3">操作失敗或權限不足</h2>
        <p class="text-muted mb-4">
            <%= typeof message !== 'undefined' ? message : '系統發生預期外的錯誤，請稍後再試。' %>
        </p>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary px-4">返回首頁</a>
        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline-secondary px-4">重新登入</a>
    </div>

</body>
</html>